overview: Kylie is coming to terms with being transgender but is worried her girlfriend Freya will leave her if she finds out. Out of fear she continues to present as male until a mysterious alien entity body snatches her and forces her to transition into her true self. It flips her world upside down and makes her see it was never the right way up to begin with. Truths will be unravelled and hearts will be broken. Her future is in sight and it's about to be SNATCHED.
title: Snatched!
